ricom — third-party asset notices
=================================

SDF glyph atlas
---------------
ricom bundles a signed-distance-field glyph atlas for its text engine:

    crates/backend-gl/src/glyphs.bin   (R8 atlas texels)
    crates/backend-gl/src/glyphs.rs    (dimensions + metrics, @generated)

It was generated by tools/gen-sdf-atlas from **Liberation Mono**.

Liberation Mono is Copyright (c) 2012 Red Hat, Inc., licensed under the
SIL Open Font License, Version 1.1 (https://openfontlicense.org).
"Liberation" is a trademark of Red Hat, Inc.

Only the derived SDF atlas is bundled here; the font file itself is not
redistributed. To regenerate from a different font, run:

    cargo run --release --manifest-path tools/gen-sdf-atlas/Cargo.toml -- \
        <font.ttf> crates/backend-gl/src/glyphs
